@database CLIMaster.guide

@node Main


                             CLIMasterII

              The Directory Utility © Graham Maddox 1997

Introduction

CLIMaster is a friendly, intuitive and versatile directory utility
which has power matching others of many times its size. It is perfect
for use in a low memory or low disk space environment.

